Music And Soul Sundays presents MARCUS HARVEY

Join us this Sunday, 26 November for our last #MusicAndSoulSundays for 2023. As we come to an end of what has been a beautiful journey of showcasing the best of talents in South Africa. What a blessing it has been to give the artists we love and appreciate a platform to share their stories and music in a relaxed and enjoyable atmosphere.

We’ve invited the amazing @iammarcusharvey to grace our stage for the first time with his incredible vocal, rapping, producing, and songwriting abilities. Born in Alexandra, Gauteng, Marcus has made an impact with his unique approach to music and stands out as one of the most exciting voices of this generation. 

For just R300, you get to experience a live performance by Marcus Harvey, a delicious welcome drink cocktail by @jagermeistersouthafrica , savoury bar snacks, and an afterparty with sounds by @wearejayem 

Don’t miss out on a day of soulful tunes, delectable drinks, and savoury snacks curated to perfection - book your spot now with the link in bio!

With love,
The Artistry Family
